---
title: Prosciutto, Mozz & Spinach Roll-Ups with Red Pepper Mayo
description: Salty prosciutto and creamy fresh mozzarella—an Italian dream team—are wrapped up in soft tortillas with fresh spinach dressed in a sweet-tangy red pepper vinaigrette. Then they’re sliced into pretty pinwheels perfect for sharing (or not!) and served with more delicious spinach salad. This little slice of Italy takes only a few minutes to prepare—perfetto!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/prosciutto-mozz-spinach-roll-ups-d0991c90.jpg
